description:
T2 Acer Prune a few branches away from street sign and window to house. 

T1 Wisteria Cut any branches above windowsill on firstfloor. 

T3 Mimosa Remove all deadwood and reduce remaining crown to rebalance tree. 

T4 Lime tree Cut to boundary.
